  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要设计一个教育平台的核心页面流转图。主要涉及五个页面模块：ContentCDN、GradeSync、ClassroomService、StudentDB，还有一个重复的ContentCDN入口。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "P1",
        "P2",
        "P3",
        "P4",
        "P5"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "我注意到您提到了两次ContentCDN，P1和P4都是Education_ContentCDN，这是设计成两个独立入口，还是同一个服务的不同访问点？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "P1",
        "P4"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，P1是内容分发的主入口，P4是备用入口，两者最终都会汇聚到P6。P1先连到GradeSync做成绩校验，然后到ClassroomService，再到StudentDB。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "P1",
        "P2",
        "P3",
        "P5",
        "P6"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我已经把Pages子图画好了，P1→P2→P3→P5→P6，同时P4也直连到P6。这样两个ContentCDN入口就汇合了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Pages",
        "P1",
        "P2",
        "P3",
        "P4",
        "P5",
        "P6"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "接下来需要设计权限可见性控制。P6之后要进入一个Visibility判断层，有两个关键节点：V1是ContentCDN的权限校验，V2是ClassroomService的可见性控制。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "P6",
        "V1",
        "V2"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "V1和V2用菱形判断节点对吧？V1处理authorized和unauthorized两种状态，然后V2再根据true/false分支？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "V1",
        "V2"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错。V1 authorized的时候流向V2，V2为true就渲染StudentDB，为false或者V1 unauthorized都隐藏到LMS Portal。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "V1",
        "V2",
        "RENDER",
        "HIDE"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "Visibility子图已完成，P6连到V1，V1 authorized分支到V2，V2 true到RENDER节点，false到HIDE；V1 unauthorized也到HIDE。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Visibility",
        "V1",
        "V2",
        "RENDER",
        "HIDE"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "最后加上缓存层。RENDER之后要经过Caching，C1是ClassroomService缓存，C2是ContentCDN缓存，形成RENDER→C1→C2的链式结构。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "RENDER",
        "C1",
        "C2"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "Caching子图已添加，RENDER连接到C1，再连到C2。整个流程应该完整了，您看看结构对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Caching",
        "C1",
        "C2"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "等等，我发现P4的命名有问题。P4应该是Education_LMS_Portal而不是ContentCDN，我之前说错了。P4作为备用入口，实际上是门户页。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "P4"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "但这样的话HIDE节点也是Education_LMS_Portal，P4和HIDE会重名冲突。您确认P4要改成LMS_Portal吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "P4",
        "HIDE"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 13,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "不对，我搞混了。P4保持Education_ContentCDN不变，HIDE才是Education_LMS_Portal。P4和P1都是CDN入口，只是路径不同。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "P4",
        "HIDE"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 14,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "明白了，P4保持ContentCDN。那HIDE节点标注为Education_LMS_Portal，RENDER是Education_StudentDB，这样区分就清晰了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "P4",
        "HIDE",
        "RENDER"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 15,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "还有个小调整：V1到V2的authorized边，和V2到RENDER的true边，标签要显式标注出来，方便开发理解权限流转。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "V1",
        "V2",
        "RENDER"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 16,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加边标签：V1--|authorized|V2，V2--|true|RENDER，V2--|false|HIDE，V1--|unauthorized|HIDE。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "V1",
        "V2",
        "RENDER",
        "HIDE"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 17,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "C1和C2的命名我再确认下：C1是Education_ClassroomService，C2是Education_ContentCDN，对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "C1",
        "C2"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 18,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是的，C1对应ClassroomService缓存，C2对应ContentCDN缓存。RENDER→C1→C2的链路完整。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "C1",
        "C2",
        "RENDER"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 19,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "P6的命名也需要明确，它是Education_ContentCDN，作为两个入口的汇聚节点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "P6"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 20,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "P6已标注为Education_ContentCDN。现在Pages里有P1-P5和P6，其中P1和P4都是ContentCDN，P6也是，这是设计意图吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "P1",
        "P4",
        "P6"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 21,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是的，ContentCDN在教育平台里有多个角色：P1是主内容入口，P4是备用入口，P6是汇聚后的统一CDN节点。这样设计是为了高可用。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "P1",
        "P4",
        "P6"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 22,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "P5是Education_StudentDB，它直接连到P6，然后P6进入Visibility。但StudentDB通常是比较重的数据层，这样设计流转合理吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "P5",
        "P6"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 23,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "合理。P5 StudentDB之后进入P6 CDN做数据加速，然后V1做权限校验，这是为了保障学生数据的访问安全和性能。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "P5",
        "P6",
        "V1"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 24,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "整个流程图已完成。Pages、Visibility、Caching三个子图结构清晰，所有节点命名和边关系都已按您的要求落实。",
